title: BIP 11: DIGG Token Design
body:
TL;DR Proposal to decide the winners of the DIGG logo design contest. With this official snapshot, please vote for the logo that you think best represents the DIGG token for BadgerDAO. The design with the most votes will be declared the new official logo of the future DIGG token. The entries are listed in no particular order.

As discussed in https://forum.badger.finance/t/bip-11-digg-token-design/996?u=defifrog, we are moving the vote to a snapshot now that we have received majority support to ratify the selection committee's top 10. 

Please see BIP 11 in the forum to see the order of logos and to vote for your favorite design!
author: 0xa001B5639e4ed26dF58367016eB08850e3e55655
